Notes:

Click on the Historic Site name above to see pictures and a description. Click on the Latitude Longitude coordinates to go to a Google Map of the single site. (click on "Directions" and fill in your current location to get navigation directions to the site). For maps containing all sites see the map links above.

GPS coordinates were obtained from maps as well as from a GPS device. Sometimes the location reported will be on the street closest to the site, and, if estimated from a map, it may be directly located in the private property space itself. Should you discover any large errors please report them.
